description: An illustration of a tic-tac-toe board which shows a game in progress: there are two black Xs (one in the top right space and the other in the center right space) and two red Os on the board (one in the dead center of the board and the other in the bottom left space). The board itself is a muted yellow color with light blueish-green lines dividing each space.
